cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.IR 

This paper deals with automatic understanding of human affect using visual signals, which is a problem related to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the use of deep neural architectures, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper focuses on the development of expressive emotional descriptors, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
